element.text: HELLO AND WELCOME TO RAVIOLI BURGLAR SIMULATOR. HERE WE WILL GO OVER THE BASIC IDEAS OF THIS GAME. AND BY "IDEAS" I MEAN IDEA, BECAUSE THERE IS ONLY ONE THING TO DO IN THIS GAME: STEAL RAVIOLI. JUST TOUCH IT TO COLLECT IT.
